## CLI Pattern
All skills follow: `uv run python .claude/skills/<name>/<name>.py <subcommand> [args]`
Use `--help` on any script for available subcommands.

## Web Search
- Use the `alhazen_search` MCP tool (from the alhazen MCP server) for all web searches.
- Do NOT use the built-in `web_search` — it requires API keys that are not configured.
- The `alhazen_search` tool queries SearXNG (self-hosted) and returns results from Google, DuckDuckGo, and Bing.

